title: AHS Murder House S1x04 "Halloween: Part 1" | American Horror Story Murder House Reaction
author: Steph Leone
comment: Please do season 2, I love seeing your reactions and the clips of the show. I’m a huge baby when it comes to horror and I love being able to watch the episodes like this and your humor helps to ease the tension!

Consider me subbed ❤️💯 and idk if you watch anime but would love to see you react to sword art online or 7 deadly sins just suggestions lol whatever you choose I'm sure it'll be fire 🔥 but would love to see your take as a women on them non the less or you could do a series like harry potter or star wars ⭐✨
Do you want to do reactions to other seasons ?
description:
I'm back with another American Horror Story season 1 reaction video today. This week's episode is "Halloween, Part 1." Every episode gets more and more intense and I'm seriously so excited to see what this entire season of Murder House has to offer.

*also, I just noticed after my video went live that one of my parts got cut out and shortened but it wasn’t like that when I uploaded it, so I’m not sure what happened. Sorry about that!!

If you like AHS or movie reaction channels, be sure to subscribe to my channel! I put out videos every Thursday. If you have any requests for other movies or shows you want me to watch, let me know in the comments. Also, if you want me to react to other seasons of American Horror Story, let me know which ones you want to see! Thanks for watching!
